  "texts": [
    "Overall, it is practical to run our scheduler at a high frequency for handling high network dynamics in typical edge scenarios.",
    "We also analyze the effectiveness of the DNN prefetching strategy.",
    "We consider the same settings under the two real-world network traces, where DNNs must be adapted more often to handle frequently changing bandwidth.",
    "In this case, the DNN hit ratio is around 92.37% when five DNNs (out of 16) and 83.61% when only three DNNs are prefetched at a time.",
    "On our setup, such a hit ratio translates to a maximum gain of 3% in processing requests precisely with the newly selected DNN."
  ],
